    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Straightforward, affordable transportation with real value for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains a practical option for someone seeking a low-cost commuter, a first project car, or dependable basic transportation on a budget. Priced to reflect its condition, it offers an accessible entry point with plenty of upside for an owner willing to put in a little care.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without the drama? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants reliable transportation at a sensible price. It\u2019s got honest character, plenty of usefulness left, and would make a great runaround, first car, or little project for someone who enjoys getting good value. If you want something straightforward and easy on the wallet, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid project potential. It shows its age cosmetically, but the powertrain still delivers usable performance and the chassis feels like a worthwhile platform for someone who knows their way around maintenance. Good candidate for a commuter, winter beater, or enthusiast build\u2014priced to move and sold as an affordable entry point rather than a showroom piece. If you want something inexpensive with real mechanical character, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Rough around the edges, but gets the job done. Cheap entry car. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real old-school character\u2014the kind of ride that still turns an ordinary drive into a little adventure. It has the honest, broken-in feel of a machine that\u2019s lived a life and still has stories left to tell. Perfect for someone who sees charm where others see a blank canvas, whether you want an affordable set of wheels, a hands-on project, or something with unmistakable personality. If you\u2019ve been looking for a vehicle with presence, potential, and a price that makes room for your own vision, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an affordable way to get behind the wheel without overspending. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who appreciates straightforward value, whether for basic transportation, a backup vehicle, or a project opportunity. Priced to reflect its condition, it presents a practical option for someone seeking low-cost ownership.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with some life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation or a solid little project. It shows its age and has its share of wear, so I want to be upfront about that, but for the right buyer it could be a practical buy without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want cheap, honest motoring.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong bones and a surprisingly eager drivetrain. Engine starts, runs, and pulls with good torque, and the transmission engages as it should. The chassis feels straightforward and honest, making this an excellent platform for a budget build, commuter rehab, or parts donor with plenty of useful life left in the hard parts. Cosmetic wear, age-related imperfections, and deferred items are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want an affordable entry point into a workable, mechanically promising vehicle, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
